      <title>西澳大利亚皮尔巴拉港口因飓风警报关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/ports-close-off-western-australia-s-pilbara-amid-cyclone-warning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于热带气旋肖恩在西澳大利亚铁矿石资源丰富地区沿岸形成，皮尔巴拉港务局于周六晚关闭了丹皮尔港、阿什伯顿港、瓦拉努斯岛港和普雷斯顿角西港。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/ports-close-off-western-australia-s-pilbara-amid-cyclone-warning</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 04:01:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
